{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-html-video-player/step-8","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-html-video-player","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 8","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možda ste primetili da niste povezali na stvarni video. To ćete uraditi u sledećoj fazi. Kada je reč o tipovima video fajlova, postoje razlike u podršci pregledača. Da bi se to podržalo, možete koristiti elemente <code>source</code> unutar elementa <code>video</code>, a pregledač će izabrati prvi kompatibilan <code>source</code>.</p>\n<p>Evo primera elementa <code>source</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;video controls width=\"250\">\n  &#x3C;source src=\"src-url-goes-here\" type=\"video-type-goes-here\" />\n&#x3C;/video>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Element <code>source</code> je prazan element (void element), pa nema zatvarajući tag.</p>\n<p>Dodajte element <code>source</code> unutar vašeg elementa <code>video</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"68f1fac259a4afabb478b960","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-html-video-player/step-8"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Working with the HTML Video Element</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Working with the HTML Video Element</h1>\n  <video\n    width=\"640\"\n    loop\n    controls\n    muted\n    poster=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/past-event2.jpg\"\n  >\n    \n  </video>\n</body>\n</html>","head":null